@TOC Toolbox
@PREV OM_ROT_CONTROL
@NEXT OM_SIZE_CONTROL

@{b}@{u}Tool:	Scale@{uu}@{ub}

@{u}Hotkey: s@{uu}

	The @{b}Scale@{ub} tool can change the size and proportions of objects in
flexible ways, allowing special effects such as mirroring and inverting
objects.

/****** THE HELP FILES HAVE BEEN ABRIDGED FOR THIS DEMO RELEASE. ******/

	Shift-clicking on the @{b}Scale@{ub} tool opens the @{" Scale Control " link OM_SIZE_CONTROL}
requester.

@ENDNODE


@NODE OM_SIZE_CONTROL
@TITLE "The Scale Control Requester"
@TOC Toolbox
@PREV OM_SCALE
@NEXT OM_CHANGE


/****** THE HELP FILES HAVE BEEN ABRIDGED FOR THIS DEMO RELEASE. ******/

@ENDNODE


@NODE OM_CHANGE
