@TOC Toolbox
@PREV OM_SIZE_CONTROL
@NEXT OM_GETSTYLE

@{b}@{u}Tool:	Change@{uu}@{ub}

@{b}Hotkey:	C@{ub}

	Select the @{b}Change@{ub} tool to change the attributes of the currently
selected objects.  

/****** THE HELP FILES HAVE BEEN ABRIDGED FOR THIS DEMO RELEASE. ******/

	Shift-clicking on the @{b}Change@{ub} tool performs the @{" Get Style " link OM_GETSTYLE} option
of this tool.

@ENDNODE


@NODE OM_GETSTYLE
@TITLE "The Get Style Tool"
@TOC Main
@PREV OM_CHANGE
@NEXT OM_GROUP

@{b}@{u}Tool:	GetStyle@{uu}@{ub}

@{u}Hotkey: Not available@{uu}

	Shift-clicking on the @{" Change " link OM_CHANGE} tool performs the GetStyle
function of the @{b}Change@{ub} tool.  @{b}GetStyle@{ub}  will change the Current
Attributes to the attributes of the selected object.


/****** THE HELP FILES HAVE BEEN ABRIDGED FOR THIS DEMO RELEASE. ******/

@ENDNODE


@NODE OM_RAISE
@TITLE "The Forward Tool"
@TOC Toolbox
@PREV OM_UNGROUP
@NEXT OM_FRONT

@{b}@{u}Tool:	Front@{uu}@{ub}

@{b}Hotkey:	Not available@{ub}

	Select the @{b}Front@{ub} tool to move a selected object to the front of the
object immediately ahead of it.

	If you shift-click the @{b}Front@{ub} tool, the object will be moved all the
way to the front of its layer.

@ENDNODE


@NODE OM_FRONT
@TITLE "The Front Tool"
@TOC Toolbox
@PREV OM_RAISE
@NEXT OM_LOWER


/****** THE HELP FILES HAVE BEEN ABRIDGED FOR THIS DEMO RELEASE. ******/

@ENDNODE


@NODE OM_LOWER
@TITLE "The Backward Tool"
@TOC Toolbox
@PREV OM_FRONT
@NEXT OM_BACK

@{b}@{u}Tool:	Back@{uu}@{ub}

@{u}Hotkey:	Not available@{uu}

	Select the @{b}Back@{ub} tool to push a selected object to the back of the
object immediately behind it.

	If you shift-click on the @{b}Back@{ub} tool, the object will be moved all
the way to the back of its layer.

@ENDNODE


@NODE OM_BACK
@TITLE "The Back Tool:
@TOC Toolbox
