	Choosing the @{b}Settings/Default Page...@{ub} menu item opens a requester
identical to @{" Project/Page Setup... " link FM_PAGE}; and is used in the same way.  However,
here it is used to set the page layout attributes of the default project.
These are the attributes of the "Untitled" page created by the @{" Project/New " link PM_NEW}
menu item.


/****** THE HELP FILES HAVE BEEN ABRIDGED FOR THIS DEMO RELEASE. ******/

@ENDNODE


@NODE SM_EDIT
@TITLE "Settings/Edit Prefs..."
@TOC Main
@PREV SM_PAGE
@NEXT SM_FONTMGR

@{u}@{b}Menu Item:	Settings/Edit Prefs...@{ub}@{uu}

@{b}Command Key:	Right_Amiga-E@{ub}

	Choosing the @{b}Settings/Edit Prefs...@{ub} menu item opens the Edit Prefs
requester.  Use this requester to set global editing preferences that effect
all projects.

/****** THE HELP FILES HAVE BEEN ABRIDGED FOR THIS DEMO RELEASE. ******/

@ENDNODE


