@{b}@{u}Keyboard Short-Cuts@{uu}@{ub}

	The Command-Key shortcuts for menu items are displayed in the menus.
There are other Hotkeys available for the tools of the Toolbox, opening the
utility windows, setting object attributes, canceling operations, forcing
screen refreshes, etc.  Note that the hotkeys listed below are case-
sensitive.


