	@{"  r  " link OM_ROTATE}@{"  s  " link OM_SCALE}
	@{"  t  " link OM_FRONT}@{"  C  " link OM_CHANGE}
	@{"  b  " link OM_BACK}@{"  Rx " link OM_REXX} (The Rx tool can be configured to the Control-Key
				and macro of a user's choice)


