The @{" Return " link OM_ACCEPT} Key		The @{" Backspace " link OM_BACKSPACE} Key
The @{" Esc " link CC_CANCEL} (Escape) Key		The @{" Help " link HelpKey} Key
The @{" Spacebar " link SPACEBAR}			The @{" Cursor " link VM_LEFT} Keys


